name: The Incredible Adventures of Moebius Goatlizard DX
overview: The Incredible Adventures Of Moebius Goatlizard was released in 2013. The DX version with music and some other improvements was released a year later. For most of the game, you will hear the protracker module "Ace on a spring" by Stefan Winterstein, a remix of the "Thing on a Spring" theme by Rob Hubbard. It was used with permission of the author. In the game you must collect the aliens and avoid the explosive devices.
